BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
a.  [`[$a] + [$b] = [$ans1]`] ties.  Use the additive principle.


a.  [`[$a] \cdot  [$b] = [$ans2]`]  ties. Use the multiplicative principle
a.  [`[$c] \cdot ([$d]+[$f]) + [$g] = 42`] outfits.   



